message.content:
1. GH levels were measured with lanreotide Autogel® and lanreotide microparticles.
2. The mean GH level with lanreotide Autogel® was 3.8 ng/ml.
3. The standard error (SE) for the GH level with lanreotide Autogel® was 0.5.
4. The mean GH level with lanreotide microparticles was 4.3 ng/ml.
5. The standard error (SE) for the GH level with lanreotide microparticles was 0.5.
6. The GH levels were lower with lanreotide Autogel® than with lanreotide microparticles.
7. The difference in GH levels between lanreotide Autogel® and lanreotide microparticles was statistically significant (P < 0.001).
